1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
Did you know that your brain's connections are shaped by activity?

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:10,400
This idea, known as the Hebbian principle, states that neurons that fire together, wire together.

3
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:14,400
When you learn something new, those neurons connect more strongly.

4
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:19,200
Recent studies suggest this process may enhance memory retention and skill acquisition.

5
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:23,200
So, practicing a skill repeatedly can literally rewire your brain!

6
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:26,000
Curious about how you can harness this?

7
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:28,400
Follow for more brain science tips!
